Gets the value of the records property.__

_This accessor method returns a reference to the live list,_not a snapshot. Therefore any modification you make to the_returned list will be present inside the JAXB object._This is why there is not a set method for the records property.__

_For example, to add a new item, do as follows:_

_getRecords().add(newItem)__
___

_Objects of the following type(s) are allowed in the list_{@link SObject }
codeText: public List<SObject> getRecords() {_        if (records == null) {_            records = new ArrayList<SObject>()__        }_        return this.records__    }
